Data controls:
	- layer of abstraction etween the DB and the BL
	- Many advantages of layers:
	- All controls derive from the same control class
		- Work just like all other server controls
	
	There are 6 data source controls that you can use to bind data to your data bound controls
	- SqlDataSource
	- LinqDataSource
	- ObjectDataSource
	- XmlDataSource
	- SiteMapDataSource
	- EntityDataSource